defaultDr Shakespearedefault: I do not need to start, but I am nearest to you, so I will.  To start with where you finished, we should talk to people with disabilities in southern countries, wherever we can and as far as we can, to get their feedback on what is a priority.  If you are asking me what 
defaultis a priority
