defaultDr Shakespearedefault: Could I just respond to Mr Hamilton’s comment about the disability movement?  Anybody who has spent time in the disability world knows that the disability movement is not perfect.  It is in fact a lot better than many movements in its efforts to make itself inclusive and representative, but disabled people are like everybody else and, if they have not personally experienced mental health conditions 
defaultthemselves
